@zloyden It's a Ramadan widget counter combined with an ad link and ad image. See related issue: https://github.com/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/issues/225370#issuecomment-3943532403 What do you think about this? 🤔 

For example suggestion filter rule (but don't know how to block ad image (eminevim):

```adb
gazetebirlik.com#$#.prayerLink[href*="eminevim"] { pointer-events: none !important }
```
